bluelatex (1.0.4-1) wheezy; urgency=low

  * Patch release mainly to fix a bug in the synchronization protocol on the
    server side, and improve the user experience on the client side.
    * Fix the guarantee delivery part in case of disconnection or high latency
      network (issue #188)
    * Hold the scroll position when several authors are editing a file
      concurrently (issue #185)
    * Restore cursor position when changing file (issue #181)
    * Fix script loading order to avoid display problems on slow networks
      (issue #189)
    * Re-enable use of standard key binings in web browser (issue #171)
    * Fix PDF rendering on small displays (issue #182)
  * Deb packaging : better version independent build script

 -- Jérôme Drouet <jerome.drouet@gmail.com>  Tue, 02 Dec 2014 11:50:34 +0100

