bluelatex (1.0.3-1) wheezy; urgency=low

  * Patch release to fix some really annoying bugs and a bug regression.
    * Add button to cleanup compilation directory (issue #173)
    * Reload pdf file when compilation failed but produced a new pdf file
      (issue #168)
    * Fix regression bug in web client making it impossible to modify user
      settings (issue #175)

